text.en_US: Jump pad launch heights can be set independently of whatever level is above them.
Be sure to check how much height you can get with them!
This one goes a bit short of the ledge at the end.
If you don't long jump your launch direction will be locked.
Try long jumping from the jump pad to the other block.
And do not long jump as soon as you leave the ledge! Try slashing later in the jump.
